Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
At Parkway we provide you top-class facilities with luxuriously built sports grounds, a state-of-the-art gym, an exceptional food court and inspiring coworking space. Situated right at the heart of kalamassery, our main focus is on changing the face of Kochi’s recreational culture.

Here we have internationally certified courts for your favourite games including cricket, football, basketball and beach volley. In fact, we have the only beach volley court in all of Kerala. Our aim is to make our clients experience the aura of real professional games.

We also have a state-of-the-art gymnasium with large facilities and top-line pieces of equipment and highly professional trainers. Our restaurant has amazing food that perfectly sums up the best of local and international flavours.
